         MACRO                                                          00000100
&L       HEXITC &M                                                      00000200
         AIF   (T'&M EQ 'N').OK                                         00000300
         MNOTE *,'USE HEXIT FOR UNCONDITIONAL RETURN'                   00000400
&L       B     4(,12)         RETURN UNCONDITIONALLY                    00000500
         MEXIT                                                          00000600
.OK      ANOP                                                           00000700
&L       BC    &M,4(,12)      RETURN CONDITIONALLY                      00000800
         MEND                                                           00000900
